Rene Bernal De LEON-SAMAYOA, Petitioner, v. IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE, Respondent. No. 00-71406. I & NS No. A28-777-689. United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Argued and Submitted Feb. 7, 2002. Decided Feb. 13, 2002.

*356Before TROTT, THOMAS and WARDLAW, Circuit Judges.

ORDER *

The Petition for Review is Denied.
